description._content: Title: Mission Concepcion. 1st Mission. Alternative Title: [Mission Nuestra Senora de la Purisima Concepcion de Acuna] Creator: Mary E. Jacobson Date: ca. 1892 Part Of: Album of views of Arizona, New Mexico and the southwest, 1892 Place: San Antonio, Bexar County, Texas Description: This photograph is part of an album containing photographs of Arizona and New Mexico by William Henry Jackson, as well as photographs of San Antonio, Texas, by Mary E. Jacobson.
